7886,"STATEMENT BY PHILIP J. CROWLEY
ASSISTANT SECRETARY OF STATE FOR PUBLIC AFFAIRS
Update on Ambassador Richard Holbrooke
Ambassador Richard Holbrooke was admitted to George Washington University Hospital yesterday. This morning,
doctors completed surgery to repair a tear in his aorta. He is in critical condition and has been joined by his family.
